com.thinkaurelius.titan.core

Interface TitanProperty

  • All Superinterfaces:
    com.tinkerpop.blueprints.Element, Idfiable, Removable, TitanElement, TitanRelation
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractProperty, CacheProperty, StandardProperty

    public interface TitanProperty
extends TitanRelation
    TitanProperty is a TitanRelation connecting a vertex to a value. TitanProperty extends TitanRelation, with methods for retrieving the property's value and key.
    Author:
    Matthias Bröcheler (me@matthiasb.com);
    See Also:
    TitanRelation, PropertyKey
